      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a fair-condition car, suitable for buyers seeking affordable, functional transportation who are comfortable with a vehicle that shows its age. The exterior displays visible wear including minor dents, surface scratches, and some paint fading consistent with years of regular use. The interior is functional but worn \u2014 expect faded upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and general signs of daily use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near future. No major mechanical failures are present, but this is not a like-new vehicle. Ideal for a practical buyer who wants reliable transportation without paying a premium price.",
