    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Solid & Straightforward \u2013 An Honest Fair-Condition Pick! \ud83d\ude99\n\nLooking for a no-nonsense vehicle that gets the job done without the premium price tag? Here's your chance! We'll be completely upfront: this car is in fair condition, meaning it runs and drives reliably but does show its age with some visible wear, minor cosmetic blemishes, and the kind of character you'd expect from a well-used vehicle. It's not showroom-perfect \u2014 but it's honest, functional, and priced to reflect exactly what you're getting. Great for a budget-conscious buyer who needs dependable transportation without any surprises. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent so you can make a well-informed decision before purchasing. The exterior is in rough shape \u2014 expect significant rust on multiple body panels, deep scratches, dents, and paint that has faded and peeled in several areas. The interior shows heavy wear throughout, including torn upholstery, cracked dashboard components, and worn-out carpeting. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention, and we recommend a thorough pre-purchase inspection by a qualified mechanic. This car is best suited for a buyer who is comfortable with a project vehicle or is looking for parts. It is priced accordingly to reflect its current state, and we encourage all interested buyers to view it in person so there are no surprises.",
      "price": 4500.0,
